ger\nsystems, however, the deviations between harmonic and exact $J$ values increase\napproximately linearly with size.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 10 Jun 2015 17:17:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 28 Jul 2015 23:02:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-07-30"}
