wcasing multiple perspectives, such as ours,\nprovide policymakers with better insights for effective responses for poverty\neradication.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 10 Jun 2015 17:21:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-11"}
